{"tid":762490,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"余香凝自爆中三有初戀男友","createTime":"2018-07-31T10:29:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-01T17:22:20.000Z","uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"27eac04857f58e763d6f4135e1536d80f7366b53","tid":762490,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T10:29:40.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】余香凝、岑珈其、導演歐文傑前晚出席電影《非同凡響》優先場。余香凝表示戲裏與岑珈其飾演中學生，憶起自己讀小學時經歷反叛期，她說﹕「媽媽外出工作，我偷偷出街玩，夾埋妹妹講大話，叫妹妹說我睡了覺；直至升中學才乖乖地讀書。」她指媽咪算開通，沒反對她在求學期結識男朋友，她說﹕「我的初戀在中三！」余香凝稱學生時代曾做暑假工賣漢堡包。岑珈其透露14歲已踩單車送外賣掙零用錢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180731/s00016/1532974786506\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180731%2Fs00016%2F1532974786506&d=PHC3uQZ8Qvt1qIW%2FsaJPAy7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=8c1a7277\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180731%2Fs00016%2F1532974786506&h=897d43e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180731/s00016/1532974786506</a><br />\n<br />\n明報又收咗幾多宣傳費？係咁幫套劇宣傳"},{"pid":"e2ec71487c728309a9ca6f375ee6c1a8e2ed9e43","tid":762490,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T10:42:28.000Z","msg":"喜歡黑黝黝健康膚色 余香凝：向古天樂膚色進發 <br />\n余香凝和胡子彤昨晚出席電影《逆流大叔》首映禮，余香凝表示早前出席紐約電影節時，已看過《逆》片，覺得自己的膚色黑到「令」。胡子彤笑余香凝曬黑是為美白代言人鋪路，可惜無人問津。<br />\n余香凝不介意膚色太黑，反而喜歡黑黝黝的健康膚色，她說：「我會繼續曬，向古天樂膚色進發。」胡子彤也喜歡黑黝黝的膚色，可以突顯肌肉線條，可是面上搽了防曬關係，搞到整個人變得兩截色，身體更黑過塊面。余香凝更取笑胡子彤拍攝時經常赤裸上身，胡子彤解釋是導演不准他著衫，並非自己想暴露。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz3.php?nodeid=1533023173774&amp;subcate=latest&amp;issue=20180731\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz3.php%3Fnodeid%3D1533023173774%26subcate%3Dlatest%26issue%3D20180731&d=PHC3uQZ8Qvt1qIW%2FsaJPAy7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=bdc76b5a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz3.php%3Fnodeid%3D1533023173774%26subcate%3Dlatest%26issue%3D20180731&h=85c69acd\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz3.php?nodeid=1533023173774&amp;subcate=latest&amp;issue=20180731</a>"},{"pid":"5070da110812f6860a4b13bcd3cf618f075b7a01","tid":762490,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T10:48:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"45a6628ab38e11cc46f21415e5c3ae2296889c26","tid":762490,"uid":2470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T10:48:34.000Z","msg":"閪是臭的"},{"pid":"1baf2efa63f8ee668dae27ab23965518fc0de7b2","tid":762490,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5070da110812f6860a4b13bcd3cf618f075b7a01","tid":762490,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T10:48:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T10:49:14.000Z","msg":"冷凍人個ex"},{"pid":"f1214ade210fa9ab787b41b90c82e3abc58419a2","tid":762490,"uid":142872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T10:49:46.000Z","msg":"?"},{"pid":"1db10a191a8296f2aebedf2b129a5dcfd83f5454","tid":762490,"uid":173195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T17:22:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}